<br>
The advantages for a cleric are huge:<br>
<br>
Safe fall as mentioned above<br>
Can open spell book without SitAggro(tm)<br>
Can med without SitAggro(tm) - as long as you aren't moving, you're medding.<br>
Can cast from spellbook<br>
Seem to med while casting but I'm still unsure if thats a client update dealie like tick medding is<br>
Always on speed - horse zones with you as long as the zone is flagged sowable. Buttercup, my war pony, disappeared when I zoned into KC but I could resummon inside. That's the only dungeon+sowable zone I've been to (ymmv in Hate, Unrest, CT, Skyshrine etc; )<br>
<br>
Disadvantages:<br>
<br>
'Spensive !<br>
Riding learning curve since horse walks, trots, then gallops as opposed to jboots where you just stand up and immediately are running. Strafing and turning have to be done a bit different on horse as well.<br>
Horseys don't like water - they disappear if they have to swim<br>
You can't follow anyone while mounted, but they can follow you.<br>
Can't be lev'd, but spells that have multi-components like bard travel song and the druid lev/sow spell gives the other benefits.<br>
Cloudy potions don't take effect while mounted but you can have invis cast on you from another or use larrikans.<br>
Hard to target with the mouse (horse's head is always in the way) and hard for others to target you in the same way ( they target XX's mount). <p><DIV align=center><A href=http://www.kyid.net target=top><FONT face=Tempus Sans ITC alias color=#33cccc ><img src=http://ldnews.kyid.net/images/members/derenath.jpg></A><BR>Derenath 60 Dwarven Cleric<BR>Theek 51 Ogre Warrior<BR>Lumiere Divine</DIV></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/uderenath1.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Derenath1</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.plauder-smilies.de/beerchug.gif" BORDER=0> at: 1/2/02 1:22:23 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#564E39><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/uauruspex.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Auruspex</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Yuri's the name...</span><br>  Posts: 171<br> <font color=#F4CC10>(1/2/02 1:54:33 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fthecrossroadstavern8833frm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=774.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: TBoots, JBoots, or a horse</span><hr size=1> aye rex.. send me a tell if you want the MQ.. ill sell it for the going price whatever that is and even get you the rapier! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><img align="left" src="http://troop475.hypermart.net/EQ/yuripic1.jpg"><i><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=63653">Yuri</a><BR>
